Reference for the basic of Cron:
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-use-cron-to-automate-tasks-ubuntu-1804

sudo apt install cron
sudo systemctl enable cron

This is the syntax for the cron job
	minute hour day_of_month month day_of_week command_to_run

Edit cron jobs
	crontab -e

Don't edit this
This is the plase where the root of the jobs stay.
	sudo nano /etc/crontab

Remove the all cron jobs
	crontab -r

Display cron config file
	crontab -l

